     }

     }

     public function setEmail($email) {

        $this->email = $email;

        return $this;   
     }

     }

        $this->password = $password;

        return $this;
     }

     public function getPassword() {

        return $this->password;

     }

     public function setAdmin($admin) {

        $this->admin = $admin;

        return $this;
     }

     public function isAdmin(): bool  {

        return $this->admin;
     }
